#!/usr/bin/env bash
# Shebang for better file detection
#### RatOS module config
#### Written by Mikkel Schmidt aka miklschmidt <mikkel.schmidt@gmail.com>
#### Copyright 2023
####
#### Contains code from Stephan Wendel aka KwadFan <me@stephanwe.de>
